Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.87,0:01:24.61,Sign,,0,0,0,,{up to down}Riichi Mahjong\NLow Fees{低料金}\N4 players at a time {4人様歓迎 - lit: 4 people welcome - not sure}\N{same thing again every 3 stairs}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.17,0:01:24.95,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.58,0:01:26.90,Song,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.90,0:01:27.95,Song,,0,0,0,,Yeah, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.95,0:01:29.42,Song,,0,0,0,,Give me just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.92,0:01:37.08,Song,,0,0,0,,Pon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.08,0:01:39.08,Song,,0,0,0,,Oh? Calling already?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.08,0:01:41.32,Song,,0,0,0,,Early calling breeds self-destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.13,0:01:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.77,0:01:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, didn't we warn you earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.87,0:01:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Early calling breeds self-destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.67,0:01:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This ain't gonna go well for you, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It changes the flow of tiles too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.41,0:01:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Kan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.83,0:02:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.50,0:02:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,All pungs kandora through tsumo. {all pungs; winning hand consisting of four pungs or kongs and one pair​}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.49,0:02:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a haneman. {win worth 12000 points (or, if dealer, 18000 points)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk... I'm all out of luck. \NI shouldn't take it for granted next time. {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And you just needed this north as the fourth tile. All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.78,0:02:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, aren't you that mysterious mahjong rogue they talk about lately? {nc what's jangoro, seems to be some specific name they use to refer to ryuu, I suspect jan part comes from mahJANg and goro is "racketeer; thug; rogue; bully; fixer"}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Always with a cigarette in your right hand and a nervous look.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.29,0:02:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.28,0:02:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a toitoi chanta? {nc}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.76,0:02:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,涼草切っていいそぽんか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.82,0:02:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.29,0:02:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,まあどっちにしても本日か それともちゃんたか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,さてと何を切るか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.57,0:02:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,ランスを切ってイースをポンということは ペン酸素の受け入れも考えているってことはだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:03:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,ドラスは乗りランガンはやばい 新規制圧名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a war of nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what is on his mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Make a move already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.48,0:03:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The clock is ticking, \Nand it ain't just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.81,0:03:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop playing dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.04,0:03:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.16,0:03:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,ロン シャーチュントイトイマンガン
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.83,0:03:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,ど真ん中のシャンポンだと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.54,0:03:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,てめえ罠取るやつを残したら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Manager, this ain't looking good. {chapter 9}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.34,0:03:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If we put that rogue up against those guys, they'll cause some trouble for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just some punk who doesn't know his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.25,0:03:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If he keeps playing like that, \Nhe'll get himself killed anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.84,0:03:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey buddy, regret calling that already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.15,0:03:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,いちにさんの三食なら リャンソーは泣きたいとこだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.93,0:03:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.52,0:03:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There, I finally caught up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,あんちゃん カンドラめくってくれや
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, that's not bad either!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.95,0:04:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,かんしてみるもんだぜ こりゃほんとについてきやがった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,いつどいといチュンドライオン バイマン よし一気に挽回だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.09,0:04:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not in this for much longer. {lit: your back is sooty - I don't understand the metaphor, but essentially it's ryuu's way of saying "you're already dead" - in manga he's sort of like grim reaper as anyone he says this to dies soon; https://manba.co.jp/topics/21894}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.83,0:04:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.09,0:04:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, bud, you said I'm not in this for longer - what did you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.64,0:04:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better explain yourself, lest we arrive to some painful misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,かっ!どうで三活の出来上がりじゃ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.11,0:04:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Ron.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.15,0:04:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Ron?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,てめえ酸素をポンしたじゃねえか!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.62,0:05:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Asshole! Think you can get away with making fun of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.06,0:05:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Ishikawa Takashi, the second boss of the Kai Group,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.24,0:05:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,here to represent the interests of my predecessor Kai Shozo. {no clue what's shoumei}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are the Dragon. {his real name is not ryuu}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.69,0:05:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Did you say Dragon? \N{\i1}The{\i0} Calling Dragon? {popular translation of this title is "crying dragon" but I think it's a mistranslation because "naki" is used more often as "to cry" but in this case it's "to call [a combination in mahjong]", like when they shout "Ron/Tsumo" during games}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.42,0:05:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon, our boss put his life on the line while digging into it just to take a glance at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.34,0:05:50.35,Sign,,0,0,0,,Flying Legend of Mahjong \NThe Calling Dragon {麻雀飛翔伝 哭きの竜}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.99,0:06:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it, you dipshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.26,0:06:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear me telling you to stop?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.10,0:06:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.29,0:07:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,On that day, Kai Shouzou lived on within Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai Shozo raised Ishikawa Takashi and always looked after him,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.79,0:07:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,because he believed Ishikawa to be capable of carrying on his back the future
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.76,0:07:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,of Kai Group and the entire Oudou Syndicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.75,0:07:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishikawa arrived at a certain general hospital in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He was there to check on Sakurada Michizo,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.17,0:07:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the head of the Oudou Syndicate, who was shot at
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.57,0:08:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,by a member of Miyoshi Group because of their prolonged feud with the Kai Group. {I hope your brain is melting already, mine sure does}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.78,0:08:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,For Ishikawa, that meant that everyone's expectations of him were set high.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys will wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,"High expectations." {omoki omowaku - lit: "heavy heaviments" (expectations) - was used in previous line as well, it seems they're very fond of this phrase for some reason}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Namely, the dying wish of the head of the Kai Group,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.79,0:08:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,former lieutenant of the Oudou Syndicate, Kai Shozo,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,that would become his final assignment for Ishikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to ask, but could you kick that door open for me? {no idea what he means}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.03,0:08:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,With all due respect, sir, \Nthis place is run by the Kawachi Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No one is allowed to enter without boss' permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.21,0:08:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Interesting, I didn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.08,0:08:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Ishikawa, the second boss of Kai Group, \Nand yet he still won't open to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.64,0:08:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Coward! Open this door at once! {no clue what's this sanpin}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if it isn't boss Kawachi? \NLong time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:59.92,Sign,,0,0,0,,Koichi Kawachi - head of the Kawachi Group, part of the Sakurado Syndicate {桜道会系川地組組長\N川地幸一}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.44,0:09:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishikawa, what did you come here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.00,0:09:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been put in charge of boss' hospital room. It's none of your business. {I have no idea what is going on anymore so from now on I'm just gonna leave the most literal, uninspired translations - it doesn't make sense, but at least it's not wrong; I'm sure nobody among the japanese audience could tell what's going on now either so fuck it - it's not our fault the show is a mess that's impossible to follow}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.68,0:09:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to check on boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.45,0:09:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:14.40,Sign,,0,0,0,,Kawachi Group Lieutenant \NMurota Sakae {川地組 若頭\N室田栄}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.48,0:09:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you seriously telling me that you didn't know that only those
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,who shared a cup of sake with the old man can get to meet him? {oyaji is "father" but that makes absolutely no sense}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.92,0:09:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And the reason I came here today is to share a cup with the boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.16,0:09:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.43,0:09:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishikawa, who do you think you are \Nto be allowed to drink sake with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.86,0:09:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind you, it was the fight your predecessor, Kai started,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.57,0:09:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that brought our old man to this state.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.71,0:09:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishikawa, you asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishikawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.05,0:09:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not moving an inch from here until I get to share a cup with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oudou and Kai are two strongest organizations of the Eastern Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.93,0:10:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,with undisputed mastery over the Kanto region.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes the Kai Group with 2,000 men in its ranks
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the most important one among my boys. {no clue what's chokkei, assumed this is kai shozo}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.51,0:10:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't tolerate anyone messing with their "night" businesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hit them, they hit back two or three times harder. {chapter 4 of manga}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's yakuza for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not interested in listening to your boasting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.36,0:10:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.68,0:10:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Dragon. You know I'll make you mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I am quite certain that you have it in you - \Nthe thing I'm looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're absolutely fearless, \Nthat's an important gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But not as much as your extraordinary luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.30,0:10:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it ever since we first met at boss's mansion -
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.74,0:10:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you're a monster, who lives by fighting alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So? Why don't you become mine and keep growing as a player?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:11:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems, boss also has a lot of admiration for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I answer to nobody. I'm not anyone's property.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon, I carry on my back the lives of 2,000 members of Kai Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon, you shouldn't humiliate me like that with your rudeness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.20,0:11:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to set an example for everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.50,0:11:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.19,0:11:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,チー 今度はソウズの染めの助かいな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, buddy, don't get carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.11,0:11:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You may have been winning so far, \Nbut it was through sheer luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:12:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mahjong is a game you can only win if you have the skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch closely, buddy. I'm about to show you what real mahjong is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.72,0:12:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.19,0:12:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that only one thing matters in mahjong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.23,0:12:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.53,0:12:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,てめえ ソーツじゃねえのかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.23,0:12:34.75,Sign,,0,0,0,,Mahjong 2nd floor
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.32,0:12:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.31,0:12:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Gunshots?! {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.81,0:12:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon... Dragon, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon! Give me your luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.02,0:13:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to the old man, Dragon! {no clue if that's how he refers to himself}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.45,0:13:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishikawa may enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.49,0:13:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?{no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.43,0:13:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss is going to meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.43,0:13:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Shozo... {chapter 11}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.34,0:13:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, ma'am, \Ntake good care of Ishikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.44,0:13:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,With time, he'll be the only man strong enough
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to carry the fate of Oudou and Kai on his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.78,0:13:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing that can defeat him is luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If he had luck, he could be the man to rule over all of Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.75,0:13:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakurada Michizo's last child, Ishikawa Takashi, is now born.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:13:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.97,0:14:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You continuously kept refusing even my predecessor, the first boss,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but I, Ishikawa, will definitely make you play with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.67,0:14:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,With your luck, I can become the best in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.11,0:14:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, bud, how are you planning to get out of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.09,0:14:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Kan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{muzu help}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon. Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.07,0:14:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wished to spend one more joyous evening playing mahjong with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.88,0:14:49.28,Sign,,0,0,0,,Sakurada Michizo, chairman of the Sakurado Conglomerate, passes away {桜道会会長桜田道造 死去}{they're called chairmen and conglomerates to give it a veneer of being legal businesses and not organized crime}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:53.69,Sign,,0,0,0,,The next chairman is Koichi Kawachi... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Bastard! You'll regret making fun of the yakuza!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you! {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.66,0:15:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon, come with us for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss Ishikawa is determined to play against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.05,0:15:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dragon? The calling dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If you refuse...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.58,0:15:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.19,0:15:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell this to your Ishikawa: my life... \NMy very cheap life is heavily overestimated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ishikawa's goons! {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't you taking the tough image too far?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.97,0:15:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess the whole group starts acting up when the boss changes, eh?! {chapter 12}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.11,0:15:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have you know that the guy you've got a gun on is one of my men!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:16:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it, Dragon. \NWho said you can leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, it must be fate that we meet again here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long while \Nsince you last played me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Murota took Dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.76,0:16:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Murota said if you want Dragon, you must take him by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So Murota took Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.95,0:16:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy is using Dragon to try me. \NTry me, Ishikawa Takashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I deal with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.45,0:16:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How would a man whom the first boss entrusted with the lives of his 2,000 men act?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.45,0:16:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It took me ten years to be able to speak in front of the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand, dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you hate the yakuza right off the bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.87,0:16:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to the Umemiya Gambling House where we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.04,0:16:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still amazed by your method of playing even now when I remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.65,0:17:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,ぽんぽんと様なしでツイースを 積もってみせやがったっけな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.46,0:17:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.98,0:17:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that woman I rewarded you with doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.10,0:17:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I was also the one who introduced you to the boss after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Imbecile! When you meet the boss, \Nyou greet him with a bow! {no clue what's izatsuite}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.55,0:17:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The memory of his encounter with Kaito was brought back to life in Dragon's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.28,0:17:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.78,0:17:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumo.\NPinfu Ittsuu. Right. {third chapter of manga}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumo.\NTanyao Iipeiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.93,0:18:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,2,000 all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you a yakuza?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.49,0:18:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? What'd you just say, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.63,0:18:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it considered shameful for yakuza to deceive others?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.27,0:18:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you take those sunglasses off?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.14,0:18:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the fun and games are over, Shozo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.77,0:18:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems I'm losing my knack, boss. \NTo think I'd be caught by a kid of all people...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.77,0:18:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like Murota didn't even notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.26,0:18:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Boss Kai is calling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.10,0:18:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:19:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If he needs something, \Nhe can come with his own feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.84,0:19:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You prick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.21,0:19:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you can't lay a finger on that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.84,0:19:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy is mine, \Nlet him do as he pleases.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.04,0:19:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon, it's better that you don't take yakuza lightly. {chapter 12}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You can be quite well-off with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.92,0:19:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.19,0:19:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Professional gamblers deceive people for a living. {no clue what's bagujujihan}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.96,0:19:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon, aren't they the perfect prey for you? {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.57,0:19:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.87,0:19:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I hit the bull's-eye, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,それも積もって三安公の手をわざわざ崩してよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,ご苦労なこった 先天系 あんた 素直になんなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.11,0:19:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Come clean, you. {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Don't mess with me! {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.36,0:19:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.02,0:19:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,今度はリュウイーソーか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon, it seems to me you never lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.49,0:20:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But those who don't know the pain of losing, don't know what a true battle is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He who gets up first after a defeat is the strongest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.16,0:20:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon, I'm going to let you taste the anguish of defeat now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.51,0:20:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not in this for much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.14,0:20:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What do you mean I'm not in this for longer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.69,0:20:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What? \Nてめえで切ってるパイパンはポン だと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.43,0:20:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Asshole, are you even paying attention? {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.30,0:20:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't carry the burden of even a single person on your back. {chapter 8}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.79,0:20:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Unwavering faith in yourself is required to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.54,0:20:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If the taste of defeat still lingers in your mouth, you've already lost. {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.89,0:21:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawachi sent his small fry for us. {I'm gonna stop saying guess now, there are more lines that are one than there are ones where I'm certain what they're saying}{still chapter 12}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.73,0:21:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If you know that I'm the second boss of the Kai Group, Ishikawa Takashi, don't hesitate
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.77,0:21:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.44,0:21:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't hit me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.90,0:21:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This bulletproof glass is the proof the Kai Clan has nothing to fear from you! {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.18,0:21:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The conference was a mess, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.30,0:21:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Even before the memorial service for boss was over, a huge internal feud broke out. {chapter 13}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.85,0:21:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Rumor has it that some men in Kawachi Group already went missing without a trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.82,0:21:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it Kai Group who did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.75,0:21:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Some say, the Kawachi Group fabricated it themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.83,0:21:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But that guy Ishikawa Takashi, the current leader of Kai Group,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.40,0:21:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,has great acumen, isn't that what they say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon knew it full well -
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,it won't be long before Ishikawa Takashi would stand in his way himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.91,0:21:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It was his intuition of a man who had lived his whole live amidst conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.25,0:22:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon's blood was boiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.56,0:22:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.06,0:22:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,カンソル暇なしかい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.66,0:22:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Ron.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.87,0:22:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,チンチトイと言ったんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.90,0:22:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I've heard the rumors, \Nbut it seems even they don't do you justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.34,0:22:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Miyoshi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.84,0:22:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So you knew who I was from the start?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.65,0:22:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not my first game with a yakuza.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.57,0:22:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.36,0:22:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,F-Fuckers...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.40,0:22:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kai…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.54,0:22:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{Huh?}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.57,0:23:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see, Dragon. You're just one tile away from Suukantsu, eh? {muzu help}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.51,0:23:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking for you, \Nbut I also got to meet Miyoshi, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.60,0:23:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be grateful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.58,0:23:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Spare me your thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.65,0:23:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Just calling off your dogs that follow my every step would be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.55,0:23:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're as unamiable as ever. {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.12,0:23:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Motherfucker...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.53,0:23:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.92,0:23:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyoshi, it's your turn. \NWhat's taking you so long? {no clue; chapter 5}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.51,0:23:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Kan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.46,0:23:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.08,0:23:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm waiting, Dragon. \NYou and me still have a game to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.82,0:23:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon, you always play with your life on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.29,0:23:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,For that reason, I'll put my life on the line as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.73,0:23:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be our first and last life-or-death battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.73,0:24:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The battle of that night was impressed vividly into Dragon's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.14,0:24:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It was at the metropolitan office of the Oudou Syndicate
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.14,0:24:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,where Boss Sakurada invited his close associate
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.61,0:24:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Maruko Sadagoro for a game with Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.05,0:24:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.92,0:24:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.34,0:24:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon, if I win, you'll be mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.79,0:24:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you win, you're free to do whatever you want with my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.83,0:24:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.98,0:24:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.60,0:24:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{muzu help, I see meaning of haru "to become one tile away from completion"; chapter 7 for ref}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.33,0:24:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{more muzu, "nothing ventured, nothing gained"}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.18,0:24:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This was the tactic that Maruko taught Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.78,0:24:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.14,0:24:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That night, it was as though Kai pulled tiles at will. He had heavens on his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.16,0:24:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.83,0:25:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.53,0:25:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.80,0:25:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.02,0:25:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.12,0:25:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,竜そんなチーをしていいのか
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.42,0:25:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,お前は羽満自家取りか三倍満相撲以外に
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.56,0:25:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,勝ち目はないんじゃぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.51,0:25:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not stealing tiles with my calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.13,0:25:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm imbuing them with life.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.86,0:25:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop meddling in my affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.10,0:25:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.83,0:25:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why on earth is Dragon waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.81,0:25:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,まさかまた勘チーピンってことはあるね
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.48,0:25:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.48,0:25:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine, I'm in luck today!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.51,0:25:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The heavens are on my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.55,0:25:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shozo!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.42,0:26:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Shozo, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.09,0:26:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.69,0:26:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit the fuck down and relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.28,0:26:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon! Let's settle this!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.57,0:26:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.70,0:26:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.61,0:26:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.34,0:26:23.03,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Shozo, think about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.50,0:26:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What a wonderful victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.09,0:26:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up, Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.70,0:26:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't forgotten about the settlement,have you?! {from manga, no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.36,0:26:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A promise is a promise! \NYou must take my life now!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.60,0:26:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.96,0:26:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have a hint of humanity in you,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.67,0:26:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,how can you leave without even acknowledging Kai's words?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.54,0:27:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My daughter... Kai's wife, \Nshe didn't tell anyone else, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.48,0:27:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A 12 mm bullet was lodged in his lung.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.29,0:27:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It needs to be taken out as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.94,0:27:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,However, he only has a fifty-fifty chance of surviving the operation...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.53,0:27:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He absolutely refused to undergo the surgery!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.80,0:27:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My daughter held onto me as she cried....
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.77,0:27:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He only has three months left...\NAnd Kai bet those three months
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.71,0:27:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.50,0:27:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say another word, old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.46,0:27:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're making me look pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.03,0:27:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Dragon?\NHurry up and take my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.25,0:27:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.62,0:27:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say that you're carrying the burden of 2,000 people on your back?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.36,0:27:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Cherish that burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.49,0:27:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.32,0:28:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.25,0:28:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Boss was shot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.25,0:28:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They sent an armed assassin?! {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.72,0:28:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai was right there with him - \Nwhat's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.29,0:28:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you humbly.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.20,0:28:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let boss perish now. {assuming sakurada is still alive and in the hospital, also don't understand a word of this highbrow yakuza dialect}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.53,0:28:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All I've done up to this point
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.07,0:28:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,was to expedite his ascent to the position of the strongest boss in all of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.76,0:28:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You may claim my own life several times over!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.04,0:28:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't let boss perish now!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.81,0:28:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you humbly...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.24,0:29:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt you might come home today.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.05,0:29:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting here for a quite while.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.57,0:29:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Auspicious Alliance, huh? \NQuite the witty name they've picked. {Koichi Kawachi's name is 幸一 (the guy in the middle), Koyu is 幸友 - "ko-friends" - took translation from manga, otherwise considered "koyu group" (chapter 14 btw)}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.57,0:29:42.58,Sign,,0,0,0,,Exclusive! {独占}\NAuspicious Alliance is formed! {友会結成!}\NChairman Koichi Kawachi, former Sakurado Conglomerate executive {会長 川地幸一 元桜道会幹部}\N{vertical}Challenge to the Sakurado Conglomerate's Kai Group {桜道会甲斐組に挑戦}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.07,0:29:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens, that stinking scum doesn't seem to know what shame is.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.65,0:29:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Men that have no shame don't deserve to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.29,0:29:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Tamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.62,0:29:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss... Today's the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.58,0:30:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so? Finally the day of his weekly visit to his mistress?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.10,0:30:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We have people on standby at her apartment complex. {going by logic, no idea what he actually says}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.55,0:30:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamura, get out of the country by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.04,0:30:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You can kick back and relax in Manila. Sounds good, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.06,0:30:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,At that moment, a seed of uneasiness\Nsprouted in Ishikawa's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.10,0:30:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.75,0:30:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He hoped to dispel that uneasiness with the ura dora...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.32,0:30:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.34,0:30:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,he couldn't find even a scrap of good luck. {from manga, nc what's tsuki}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.53,0:30:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.67,0:30:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have been a lot of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.81,0:30:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that the bait I've set up would work this well... {no clue what's wara}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.72,0:30:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems, Ishikawa also underestimates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.65,0:30:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,In other news,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.42,0:31:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,At Narita Bypass around 6am this morning, \Na car had burst into flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.85,0:31:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The passengers were all pronounced dead at the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.26,0:31:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on his personal belongings, one of the victims
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.43,0:31:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,was identified as Tamura Koichi, a member of Kai Group, part of the Oudou Syndicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.82,0:31:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Additionally, bullet marks were found on the bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.85,0:31:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Some suggest that it was related to the shootout
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.60,0:31:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that occurred at an apartment complex in Setagaya last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.84,0:31:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The authorities believe
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.14,0:31:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that this is one of a growing number of internal conflicts within the Oudou Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.54,0:31:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,An emergency investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.04,0:31:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,was launched into the Auspicious Alliance that split off from that organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.88,0:31:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This was Ishikawa Takashi's first taste
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.92,0:31:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,of humiliation, which shook his determination to the core.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.42,0:31:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It seemed like one man was looking at him
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.92,0:31:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,through a clearing in the dark clouds, sneering at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.52,0:31:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That man was not Kawachi, \Nand it was certainly not Murota....
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.68,0:32:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,2,000 lives were weighing heavily on Ishikawa's back. {chapter 15}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.55,0:32:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Dragon! Bring that goddamn Dragon to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.49,0:32:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishikawa Takashi went for the only gamble that could reinforce his intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.03,0:32:19.57,Sign,,0,0,0,,Mahjong parlor "Peaceful" \NFirst-timers and first-time visitors are welcome to come alone and have fun in peace. {お一人様でも安心して遊べる初めての方・初来店の方・大歓迎}\NFully automated {全卓・全自動 - probably refers to the tables}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.06,0:32:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I got a tsumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.57,0:32:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Honitsu ittsuu tsumo, double nan... {from manga}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.56,0:32:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A baiman!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.94,0:32:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you're out of luck today.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.68,0:32:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The point gap is almost 8,000 points now!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.55,0:32:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,どうだ この辺でサシウマ半ちゃん勝負といかねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.35,0:32:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the rate?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.30,0:32:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How does "a hand" sound? Plus time.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.75,0:32:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That is, if I win, you'll have to give me a hand, and come with me for a while... {from manga, no clue what he means}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.75,0:32:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,ローピンを勘 三食としても ローソをあんこに違いねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.07,0:33:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,サシウマかなんか知らんが これ レイチや
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.24,0:33:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Kan.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.50,0:33:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,やはりローソンはあんこだったか
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.11,0:33:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,どっちにしろローソンが通ったばかり
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.18,0:33:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,4枚目の急走が当たるとしたら 酷使しかねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.05,0:33:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.06,0:33:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,3色同ポン ドラ2 満眼
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.12,0:33:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,じゃ ゴーソンで当たりだったんじゃねえか!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.36,0:33:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That was your winning tile too, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.67,0:33:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Your boss has come up with quite the elaborate scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.64,0:33:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here under direct orders from boss Ishikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.13,0:33:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What? \NSo you just used me to test waters? {lit: I was a stallion brought close to a mare to test her readiness to mate}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.63,0:33:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, we haven't got much time. \NLet's conclude the next game at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.61,0:33:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If I win, Dragon will follow me to meet Ishikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.75,0:33:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Рe discarded a pair of the chun?! {manga}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.16,0:33:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I didn't think you'd do something so foolish...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.47,0:34:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better not be making fun of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.64,0:34:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Kan!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.18,0:34:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The only one who believes is yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.55,0:34:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The only one who you can believe in is yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.72,0:34:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing personal, but this game ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.22,0:34:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon, I'm the one who accepted boss Ishikawa's final orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.17,0:34:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,People call me a hitman...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.47,0:34:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just behave yourself and come with me to the boss's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.27,0:34:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So in the end, it seems the boss didn't have faith in either of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.21,0:34:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,However, this round isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.73,0:35:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon, excuse the ad nauseam, but I'm going to say this once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.28,0:35:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss Ishikawa made me into what i am.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.65,0:35:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If he calls something black, then it's black, even if it's actually white.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.06,0:35:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My life is entirely in boss Ishikawa's hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.16,0:35:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.56,0:35:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me have to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.76,0:35:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! They've killed Takashina?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.93,0:35:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it! Bring everyone to the main office! {literally unintelligible without manga lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.83,0:35:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishikawa, you punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.83,0:35:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.10,0:35:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.99,0:36:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon... You really are quite strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.02,0:36:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You discarded the same tiles as me in the last two rounds as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.20,0:36:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They're even in the same order. {from manga, pls check muzu}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.63,0:36:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon! Is it a coincidence, or is there some purpose to this matching game?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.49,0:36:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me your hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.74,0:36:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The tiles one discards are the outer world.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.51,0:36:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The tiles in one's hand are the inner world.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.88,0:36:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,One's insides are the one thing that can't be shown.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.74,0:36:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon, I want to see those "insides"of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.69,0:36:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.20,0:36:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you... Are you trying to mock me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.86,0:36:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.61,0:36:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Don't you know? {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.51,0:37:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What did you say?! \NThey got the chief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.35,0:37:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Underboss Murota Sakae was shot in the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.12,0:37:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Upon hearing that news,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.54,0:37:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the syndicate's adviser and a dozen of members hurried to confirm it.{chapter 17}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.22,0:37:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps due to the inclement weather, the phone line was out of service.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.19,0:37:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, they made a beeline straight for the designated hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.80,0:37:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon, my draws are getting very interesting now that I'm playing against you!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.74,0:37:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I'm grabbing hold of some of that monstrous luck of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.21,0:37:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.28,0:37:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? \NWhy isn't everyone here yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.80,0:37:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well... There was a call from the police saying that you had been shot...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.39,0:37:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You fools! \NI am clearly just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.32,0:37:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Murota! It's the end of the road!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.33,0:38:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems, where's no such thing as "impossible" for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.13,0:38:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I'm not one to believe in such fantasies! {manga, no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.01,0:38:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon! Let me introduce you to the concept of impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.51,0:38:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad, Dragon.\NJust a tanyao.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.27,0:38:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishikawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.60,0:38:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,riichi ippatsu tsumo\Ntanyao and sanankou. haneman! {muzu pls}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.80,0:38:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon! Do you see the two chrysanthemum flowers in between the doorframe?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.82,0:38:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The big one is for Murota, \Nand soon there will be one more!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.09,0:38:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Next to Murota's will be another flower - \Na deep crimson chrysanthemum!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.40,0:39:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately for you, Dragon, \NI won't let go of your luck until then!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.56,0:39:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're laughing at me, huh, Dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.24,0:39:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't given in to your luck yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.58,0:39:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore... I'm not so foolish to rely on the luck of other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.98,0:39:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You've finally gained enough momentum to start mocking me, Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.03,0:39:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! I'll take you on this round!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.50,0:39:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon wouldn't let the 2-pin get away. {muzu pls; こいつあるようなあたりだけちゃうならねぇ}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.10,0:39:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Dragon, it's a 2-pin. {muzu}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.87,0:39:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.35,0:39:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That sly Dragon... \NWhat on earth is he waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.58,0:40:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible? No... Possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.06,0:40:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.26,0:40:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I see now, Dragon. Are you doing that just to spite me at any cost? {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.72,0:40:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.82,0:40:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You truly are The Calling Dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.11,0:40:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.78,0:40:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you release a flash of light with every call.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.52,0:40:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.07,0:40:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yet another flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.47,0:40:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But no matter how hard you try, i will emerge victorious in the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.73,0:40:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon! Just give up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.81,0:40:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're torturing yourself. Stop throwing your life away. {no clue what he means}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.24,0:40:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything will become easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.75,0:40:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You will live in comfort \Nif you give your life up to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.98,0:41:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.00,0:41:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dragon, you... So you still intend to defy me?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.65,0:41:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well, Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.75,0:41:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put this syndicate's crest on the line for this bout! {/yakuza coat of arms}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.36,0:41:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,With the crest on the line, \NDragon is not going to live,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.48,0:41:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,regardless of whether he wins or loses. {unsure}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.39,0:41:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone present saw it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.49,0:41:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.63,0:41:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The south 3rd round... Dragon started with a call of the 8-sou. {muzu check}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.53,0:41:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{missing page in manga, muzu}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.76,0:41:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.76,0:41:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.55,0:42:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon! That hatsu is mine! Kan! {muzu}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.28,0:42:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai told me that getting into a calling war with you would cause nothing but trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.98,0:42:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But I won't back down anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.33,0:42:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to win the fights that you start. \NThat's...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.32,0:42:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the way of the yakuza!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.73,0:42:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not in this for longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.06,0:42:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.60,0:42:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Kan!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.84,0:42:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon...!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.09,0:42:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon... Are you going to declare a win? {muzu}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.49,0:42:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If Dragon flips over that tile, he'll be killed for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.67,0:42:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's attention was concentrated on Dragon's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.50,0:43:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.86,0:43:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep yourself together, Kitajima. \NWhy are you taking out your gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.24,0:43:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.93,0:43:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Kitajima. \NDon't let your spirits down.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.44,0:43:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What would I do if you lost your cool? {believing manga}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.67,0:43:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In a battle, winning means heaven,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.94,0:43:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and losing means hell. \NIsn't that right, Dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.85,0:43:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start the final round, Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.38,0:43:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,As the darkness disappeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.38,0:43:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the flow of time returned to the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.79,0:43:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Monotonously. \NReally monotonously.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.59,0:43:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The storm had turned to calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.66,0:43:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.39,0:44:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Kan!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.90,0:44:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon, I'm going to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.73,0:44:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kan.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.28,0:44:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.79,0:44:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Kan.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.33,0:44:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon, I finally understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.77,0:44:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You are an incarnation!\NAn incarnation sent to me by god!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.06,0:44:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see that god truly detests me!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.97,0:44:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He sent you to this world... You, Dragon! \NWith the sole purpose of humiliating me!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.48,0:44:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai Group's Lieutenant Sotoda Yuji clearing his throat was the signal to kill the Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.56,0:44:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But then suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.79,0:45:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.15,0:45:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.36,0:45:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop. Put down your guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.73,0:45:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon, please hear me out before you go away for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.27,0:45:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This match is over.\NThere's nothing left to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.93,0:45:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.89,0:45:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.24,0:45:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kitajima, what's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.17,0:45:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, you can't kill Dragon! \NDon't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.22,0:46:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That man is absolutely vital to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.05,0:46:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You must know this more than anyone else, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.49,0:46:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason he was born into this world
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.29,0:46:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,was to make you the greatest in the whole country!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.49,0:46:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of his monstrous luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.45,0:46:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, this is my last request...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.47,0:46:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't kill that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.81,0:47:36.05,Song,,0,0,0,,It's too lonely up north {北はさびしすぎるから\N南行きの汽車に乗ります\Nわたしのことは 大丈夫\Nどこかに落ちついたら 手紙を出します}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.72,0:47:42.25,Song,,0,0,0,,I'll take the southbound train
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.86,0:47:48.83,Song,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.83,0:48:00.81,Song,,0,0,0,,I'll write to you when I'm settled somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.81,0:48:06.75,Song,,0,0,0,,If you hesitate to leave me now, {いま 別れをためらえば\Nすがるしかない 女に なるわ\N愛した日々の重さに ああ耐えてます}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.75,0:48:12.85,Song,,0,0,0,,I'll be the one you'll have to cling to
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.85,0:48:27.57,Song,,0,0,0,,I've been holding on so tight to the weight of all the days I've loved you
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.57,0:48:33.77,Song,,0,0,0,,I SAY GOOD BYE
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.77,0:48:46.09,Song,,0,0,0,,I'm a lonely woman looking for a town that suits me {孤独な女に 似合の街を探します}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.88,0:49:18.95,Song,,0,0,0,,Love is always cruel {愛はいつも残酷ね\N信じすぎた者を 傷める\Nあなたにもしも逢わなけりゃ\N平凡すぎるほどの 生活をしてたわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.95,0:49:24.96,Song,,0,0,0,,It hurts those who believe in it too much
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.96,0:49:30.93,Song,,0,0,0,,If I hadn't met you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.93,0:49:42.81,Song,,0,0,0,,I'd have had a life that was a little too ordinary
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.81,0:49:48.88,Song,,0,0,0,,Now, with no one to see me off, {いま 見送る人もなく\N動きはじめる 駅舎の灯り\Nながす涙の熱さに ああ耐えてます}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.88,0:49:54.89,Song,,0,0,0,,The lights of the station house begin to move
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.89,0:50:09.50,Song,,0,0,0,,I'm enduring the heat of my tears
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.50,0:50:15.87,Song,,0,0,0,,I SAY GOOD BYE
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.87,0:50:28.19,Song,,0,0,0,,Please understand, “good bye”\NIt's a word of love{わかって下さい ”さよなら”\N愛の言葉です}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.66,0:50:36.93,Song,,0,0,0,,If I hesitate to say goodbye now, {いま別れをためらえば\Nすがるしかない 女になるわ\N愛した日々の重さに ああ耐えてます\NI SAY GOOD BYE\Nわかって下さい ”さよなら”\N愛の言葉です}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.93,0:50:42.66,Song,,0,0,0,,I'll become a woman who has no choice but to cling to you
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.66,0:50:57.58,Song,,0,0,0,,I've been so heavy with love, I've had to bear it
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.58,0:51:03.89,Song,,0,0,0,,I SAY GOOD BYE
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.89,0:51:16.66,Song,,0,0,0,,Please understand that I say goodbye\NIt's the language of love
